	The forward looking statements made by us in this Annual Report on Form 10-K, or elsewhere,
	speaks only as of the date on which they were made. New risks and uncertainties come up from time to time, and it is impossible for us to predict these events or how they may affect us. We have no obligation to update any forward looking statements
